<a href="https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/190509.The_Victors"><img alt="The Victors: Eisenhower and His Boys: The Men of World War II" src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/books/1388379074l/190509._SX98_.jpg" />
